---
// SecretsArchitecture.astro — Secrets access architecture diagram
---
<div class="sa-wrap">
  <h3 class="sa-title">The Right Architecture</h3>
  <p class="sa-sub">Applications should never store secrets. They should REQUEST them at runtime.</p>
  <div class="sa-diagram">
    <div class="sa-col sa-col--apps">
      <span class="sa-hl">Applications</span>
      <div class="sa-box">API Service</div>
      <div class="sa-box">Worker</div>
      <div class="sa-box">Cron Job</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sa-arrows"><span class="sa-al">Request secret<br/>at startup</span><div class="sa-aline"></div></div>
    <div class="sa-col sa-col--vault">
      <span class="sa-hl sa-hl--green">Secrets Manager</span>
      <div class="sa-box sa-box--vault">Vault / AWS SM</div>
      <div class="sa-features"><span class="sa-f">ACL: who can read what</span><span class="sa-f">Audit: every access logged</span><span class="sa-f">Encrypt: at rest + in transit</span><span class="sa-f">Rotate: automatic schedule</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sa-arrows"><span class="sa-al">Short-lived<br/>credentials</span><div class="sa-aline"></div></div>
    <div class="sa-col sa-col--targets">
      <span class="sa-hl sa-hl--amber">Target Systems</span>
      <div class="sa-box">PostgreSQL</div>
      <div class="sa-box">Redis</div>
      <div class="sa-box">S3 / Cloud APIs</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .sa-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .sa-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 .25rem}.sa-sub{color:#64748b;font-size:.78rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .sa-diagram{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .sa-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;min-width:110px}
  .sa-hl{color:#818cf8;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;font-family:monospace;text-align:center}.sa-hl--green{color:#4ade80}.sa-hl--amber{color:#f59e0b}
  .sa-box{padding:8px 12px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:8px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:.65rem;font-family:monospace;text-align:center}
  .sa-box--vault{border-color:#4ade8030;color:#4ade80}
  .sa-features{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px}
  .sa-f{color:#64748b;font-size:.55rem;font-family:monospace;text-align:center}
  .sa-arrows{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding-top:20px}
  .sa-al{color:#475569;font-size:.55rem;text-align:center;line-height:1.3;font-family:monospace}
  .sa-aline{width:30px;height:1px;background:#334155}
</style>
